{"n":"Mission: My Bosom Friend","lv":1,"maps":["1879310346","1879316660","1879316664"],"steps":[{"i":1,"pts":[[-73.463554,-72.31517,"1879310346"],[-72.89921,-79.20887,"1879310346"],[-72.66774,-79.41759,"1879310346"],[-34.220867,-84.3246,"1879316660"],[55.093513,73.78516],[55.090057,73.77141],[56.55209,37.831474],[56.00049,43.904217],[-34.178417,-84.61687,"1879316664"]],"t":"We sat in a simple study, each enjoying a smoke and spoke at length about our goals...."},{"i":2,"pts":[[-73.463554,-72.31517,"1879310346"],[-72.89921,-79.20887,"1879310346"],[-72.66774,-79.41759,"1879310346"],[-34.220867,-84.3246,"1879316660"],[55.093513,73.78516],[55.090057,73.77141],[56.55209,37.831474],[56.00049,43.904217],[-34.178417,-84.61687,"1879316664"]],"t":"Often he would be like this, jovial and open, a warm companion. I listened quietly and drew on my pipe...."},{"i":3,"pts":[[-73.463554,-72.31517,"1879310346"],[-72.89921,-79.20887,"1879310346"],[-72.66774,-79.41759,"1879310346"],[-34.220867,-84.3246,"1879316660"],[55.093513,73.78516],[55.090057,73.77141],[56.55209,37.831474],[56.00049,43.904217],[-34.178417,-84.61687,"1879316664"]],"t":"When it was my turn to speak he listened intently and responded...."}]}